</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/Qqnq-u6zmDI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/10/01/galaxy-s21-digital-key-with-the-genesis-gv60/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=galaxy-s21-digital-key-with-the-genesis-gv60</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>【評測】《Diablo 2: Resurrected》　忠實還原遊戲 + 畫質大幅提升</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/SaIWbJ7zUp0/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[AFLOW]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 01 Oct 2021 02:23:06 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[遊戲評測]]></category><category><![CDATA[blizzard]]></category><category><![CDATA[Diablo 2]]></category><category><![CDATA[Diablo II: Resurrected]]></category><category><![CDATA[Nintendo Switch]]></category><category><![CDATA[PlayStation 4]]></category><category><![CDATA[PlayStation 5]]></category><category><![CDATA[PS4]]></category><category><![CDATA[PS5]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1055569</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>繼《暗黑破壞神 III》之後，Blizzard Entertainment, Inc. （暴雪娛樂）終於宣佈重 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>繼《暗黑破壞神 III》之後，Blizzard Entertainment, Inc. （暴雪娛樂）終於宣佈重製 20 年前歷久不衰的神作《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》，於 9 月 24 日在 Playstation、Xbox、Switch 和 PC 上發佈。《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》包括《暗黑破壞神 II》原版遊戲及資料片《暗黑破壞神 II：毀滅之王》的遊戲內容，除了保留一切經典玩法外，在畫質、音效、界面上都有大幅提升。暴雪對這次重製遊戲表示骨灰級玩家和鐵粉絕對不會失望，事隔 20 年的作品重製得如何？就等 Unwire 為大家做評測。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062768 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_01-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_01-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_01-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_01-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_01-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_01.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲光是看到人物選單就已經想起以前的 D2</p><h2>這是天堂與地獄交界處的人間戰爭</h2><p>《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》有著原版與資料片的所有劇情，遊戲裡面同樣地提供 ACT 1-4 ，而 ACT 5 則為資料片的章節。2 代的故事是講述在一代故事結局被封印的 Diablo 經過長年歲月減弱下終於再次解開，並且把自己兩個兄長墨菲斯托與巴爾同時復甦，這次玩家再次需要飾演不同的英雄，從東方大陸再次重返地獄消滅邪惡的起源。而資料片則講述墨菲斯托與 diablo 被消毀之後，毀滅之王巴爾被發現躲藏在亞瑞特山脈，試圖污染世界之石，玩家需要立刻前往世界之石大殿阻止一切。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_02-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_02-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_02-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_02-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_02-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_02.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即使沒有把任務做完也可以過關</p><h2>重製支援 4K 60 fps 享受前所沒有的暢快感</h2><p>對於現代遊戲的標準，《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》將原作的 2D 模組以 3D 物理優化的方式進行重置，包括光暗效果、攻擊特效效果以及物品外觀。玩家可以除了看到外觀有明顯的變化外，遊戲裡的場景，甚至是收集的寶石和物品，都有進行重置。此外遊戲還配備了 4K （2160p）超高畫質解析度，雖然遊戲採用原版 25 fps 的遊戲畫面，不過玩家可以自行設定到 60 fps。而音效已經支援 dolby 7.1 環繞聲重製，這樣享受戰鬥的打擊感就更上一層。同時製作組重製原作全部 27 分鐘動畫，令到整個遊戲現代感增加。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_03-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_03-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_03-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_03-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_03-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_03.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲電腦版所顯示的畫面最為精細和華麗</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_04-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在家用機版下視覺效果也算中上</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062779" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_17-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_17-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_17-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_17-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_17-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_17.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重製原作全部 27 分鐘動畫非常值得一看</p><h2>遊戲系統沿用舊版令玩家找回初衷也成遊戲最大賣點</h2><p>《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》雖然在效能上提升，不過在遊戲機制、遊戲系統、寶物機率與原版保持一致沒有任何修改。所以老玩家以前所發掘的技能配搭，以前死靈法師的毒牙流、法師的冰火雙流、聖騎士的祝槌丁流等等，在重製版上可以重新組合出來！另外屬性版加點也是一樣，玩家從力量、敏捷、體力、精力中因應自己的職業或需求各自分配。正因為系統上保持原版，很多一些技巧仍然可以在新版使用，例如「無形打孔」「首殺」等等，讓大家更容易刷裝跟過渡前期。至於寶物機率不變的話，大家還記得喬丹之石（簡稱 SOJ）嗎？每個法師都想擁有的夢幻戒指當年機率是 1616:1，相信新版會再度掀起一波 Boss 上車潮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_11-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_11-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_11-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_11-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_11-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_11.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲技能點與原版一模一樣分三大類</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_12-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_12-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_12-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_12-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_12-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_12.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重製版新增進階屬性視窗可以了解清楚裝備的附加能力</p><h2>懷舊模式切換讓玩家重拾當年情懷</h2><p>如果老玩家覺得保留原版系統還不夠滿足，只要按「G」鍵就會變成原版的「經典模式」，20 年前的畫面即時浮現在眼前。經典模式只會修改畫面及模組，物品字體上跟界面並沒有太大對比，所以在壞舊模式上都可以玩得很歡樂。由於重製版某些場景去除了背景牆，在遊戲發現畫面過黑的問題，所以「經典摸式」成為其中一個解決方法。一鍵切換功能非常良好，玩家隨時隨地都可以用自己喜歡的模式進行遊戲，想用以前的畫面打 Boss 都絕對沒有問題！</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062777" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_15-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在重製版下有些畫面過黑的情況</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062791" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_19-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲經典模式下可以比較光明</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_09-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_09-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_09-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_09-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_09-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_09.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重製版 &#8211; 裝備界面</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_10-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_10-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_10-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_10-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_10-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_10.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲經典模式 &#8211; 裝備界面</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062782" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_05-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_05-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_05-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_05-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_05-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_05.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重製版 &#8211; 火焰之河</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_06-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_06-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_06-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_06-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_06-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_06.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲經典模式 &#8211; 火焰之河</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_07-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重製版 &#8211; BOSS 戰</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_08-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲經典模式 &#8211; BOSS 戰</p><h2>電腦版與家機版的存檔共用</h2><p>這次《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》除了電腦版外，家機版也一同同步發售。不過經測試下家機版不論在畫質、流暢度都不及電腦版。例如家機版因為不能轉伺服器，所以遇到擠擁問題只能默默地等，而 Switch 更因為機能問題容易斷線。而因為顯示問題上家機版的版面配置上也有一點差別，但是並不能無法接受，雖然暴雪有說專注研發在手製的控制上，不過真實體驗還是不太友善，例如檢取地上物品時需要移動人物一個個去看，物品袋與箱子轉移時需要一個個去點取。雖然 Switch 比較便利，不過由於角色網上跟單機是分開所以需要全程上網，外出時想用網上角色練等時亦會成為一大麻煩。加上 Switch 的優化做得不夠好，雙人連線時都會造成畫面卡頓，在手提模式時文字雖然清楚顯示不過字體很小，這很容易感到眼睛疲累。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_13-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062776" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_14-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲家機版不論在加屬性點或是整理裝備都是佔整個畫面</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062794" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_20-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_20-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_20-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_20.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ Switch 版手提模式下太部份畫要都有矇矇朧朧的情況</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1062778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-2048x1152.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_16-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲這應該是家機版最常見的句子了</p><h2>總結：現代的畫質+滿分情懷之作</h2><p>《暗黑破壞神 II：獄火重生》雖然綜合重製了畫面，但因為保留原有模式使得遊戲依然保持水準，對於老玩家一定愛不惜手，經典模式也成為了一大驚喜。存檔井用功能讓家機版玩家或是玩家多一個選擇，不過優化問題還需要有待改善，但我非常期待之後的跨機網上連線功能。雖然 20 年前玩法可能會對新玩家過於沉悶，不過對於可多人連線也可以讓老玩家與新玩家多交流。如果是新入門的玩家，為了保持畫質與流暢度，我是推薦先買電腦版本。《暗黑破壞神》之後會推出新一代與及手機版，隨著此類型遊戲越出越多，此重製無疑是為了鞏固舊玩家及吸納新玩家注意，到底這「如意算盤」能否打嚮？真的讓人拭目以待。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1062796" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_21-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_21-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_21-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_21-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_21-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Diablo2_21.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲期待天梯模式的更新</p></p><div class="feedflare">
